high_descs: turn to the left, move forward and turn to the right to face the white round table
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the table
turn around, move forward slightly and then turn left moving all the way across the room towards the door, turn to the left and face the counter
put the knife into the white coffee mug that is sitting on the counter
pick up the mug with the knife from the counter
turn right and move forward to the sink on the left, turn to the left and move to the sink
put the mug with the knife inside of it in to the sink
anns.task_desc: put a mug with a knife in to the sink

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the white table in the corner of the room.
Turn to the right and pick up the yellow handled knife, closest to the salt shaker from the table.
Turn around to the right and walk just past the counter. Turn to the left and walk to the door. Turn to the left to face the counter.
Place the knife into the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug with the knife from the counter.
Turn to the left and walk to the sink.
Place the mug and knife in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug containing a knife into the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the dining table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around and walk to the door to the right of the stove and turn left to face the counter..
Put the knife in the mug on the counter.
Pick up the mug and knife.
Turn left and go to the sink on your left.
Put the mug and knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a mug in the sink.
